  "title": "Restaurant Manager (RM001)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<p>- Manage and run the daily operations of the restaurant, ensuring that sales targets and service standards are met</p>\n<p>- Achieving the highest service standards and exceeding a high guest expectation daily</p>\n<p>- Establish good rapport with customers and handle customers' request professionally and promptly</p>\n<p>- Lead and motivate staff in achieving sales target and customer satisfaction</p>\n<p>- Plan staff rosters and provide training and coaching to staff on customer service and product knowledge</p>\n<p>- Enforce and comply with licensing, hygiene regulation, health and safety legislation and guidelines</p>\n<p>- Manage operational costs and requisite stocks/items required by the restaurant</p>\n<p>- Assess and improve restaurant profitability and to prepare and present staffing/sales reports to the General Manager in a timely manner</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>- Min 3 years of relevant experience in managing restaurant.</p>\n<p>- Present a positive and professional attitude at all times.</p>\n<p>- Can work independently and as a team player with good interpersonal skills</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
